  <brief_title>Is a Reporting System for Gastritis or Duodenitis (Modified Lanza Scale) Reproducible?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reproducibility of Modified Lanza Scale for the Reporting of Gastritis and Duodenitis</official_title>
